@node "texteditor" "Built-in Text Editor"

 Bug Reporter has a small built-in text editor for editing bug descriptions
 and  developer's  remarks.   This a very basic editor and this is the only
 part of the program which probably will change in the future.  The size of
 a  text  you can enter is limited only by available memory - everything is
 kept  as  lists.   Use cursor keys, backspace, del to edit and move around
 the text.  Click on close gadget to finish editing.
@endnode

