@node "loadgadget" "Load File Gadget"

 This  gadget  lets  you  to  load  a  new  report  file.  First you'll be
 presented wih a filerequester.  Choose the file to load and click on "OK".
 All  datas loaded or entered before will be lost and replaced by new datas
 from  loaded  file.  If the file is not a Bug Reporter file or there is a
 format  error  inside  this  file,  you'll  be  informed about it and the
 program  will  return  to main window.  Clicking "Cancel" will abort this
 operation  without any loses.

 WARNING:   reading  file  with  format  error  inside will cause problems.
 Bug  Reporter  will  try to load as much datas from that file as possible.
 In  such  case,  old  datas will be replaced by new, read from the file -
 even if loading wasn't completely succesful.

 Format  errors  in  report  file  can be generated during manual editing.
 Please,  DO NOT edit this file with a text editor if you don't want these
 errors to  appear.
@endnode

